WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:00.240 --> 02:02.760
Your girlfriend made this breakfast.

02:02.840 --> 02:04.240
You must finish it all!

02:05.160 --> 02:07.560
IMPROVING IMAGE QUALITY,
PLEASE HOLD YOUR DEVICE STEADY

02:16.720 --> 02:18.560
Zhizhi's travel plan.

02:21.120 --> 02:22.200
TRAVEL PLAN

02:24.080 --> 02:25.200
CAMPING CHECKLIST

02:25.280 --> 02:27.200
BEAUTIFUL COUNTRYSIDE

02:32.920 --> 02:36.160
YOUNG GIRLS' FAVORITE TRAVEL PLANS

02:36.240 --> 02:42.280
HIGHLY-RATED FIVE-STAR HOTELS

03:14.000 --> 03:15.280
Go back to sleep.

03:34.040 --> 03:35.560
Hello, your takeout is here.

03:36.520 --> 03:37.400
I…

03:38.200 --> 03:40.120
I didn't order any takeout. Sorry.

03:40.200 --> 03:42.400
Mr. Duan Jiaxu ordered it for you.

03:47.400 --> 03:48.720
Please give it to me. Thank you.

03:49.640 --> 03:50.840
Remember to give a good review.

03:52.080 --> 03:52.960
A good review?

03:58.520 --> 03:59.880
I ordered supper for you.

03:59.960 --> 04:02.160
DUAN JIAXU

04:06.840 --> 04:08.080
TAP TO TAKE A PHOTO,
LONG PRESS TO RECORD A VIDEO

04:14.920 --> 04:16.399
I have the same.

04:16.480 --> 04:17.600
I'll eat with you.

04:17.680 --> 04:21.079
DUAN JIAXU

04:21.160 --> 04:23.080
I'll give you

04:23.160 --> 04:24.720
a good review.

04:24.800 --> 04:27.160
SANG ZHI

04:40.640 --> 04:43.160
Listen, enjoy your meal.

04:43.240 --> 04:44.680
I want you to focus when you work.

04:44.760 --> 04:46.040
- All right.
- Okay.

04:46.120 --> 04:47.120
- No problem.
- Definitely.

04:47.200 --> 04:48.440
Xiaowan and Sang Zhi

04:48.520 --> 04:50.280
are the smartest and most capable interns

04:50.360 --> 04:51.800
that I've had in the past few years.

04:52.720 --> 04:54.400
So who is smart and who is capable?

04:54.480 --> 04:56.480
- Tell us.
- Xiaowan is smart. Sang Zhi is capable.

04:57.360 --> 04:59.080
Of all my mentors,

04:59.160 --> 05:00.320
you've doted on me the most.

05:00.400 --> 05:01.640
I like the way you talk.

05:02.520 --> 05:03.400
Well,

05:03.480 --> 05:06.920
I prepared some small gifts for everyone.

05:07.000 --> 05:09.400
Thank you for your help

05:09.480 --> 05:10.360
over the past month.

05:11.040 --> 05:13.160
- Pick out what you like.
- You're so thoughtful.

05:14.960 --> 05:15.840
Mr. Zhang.

05:17.120 --> 05:18.400
What are you guys doing here?

05:18.480 --> 05:19.840
Do I get one too?

05:19.920 --> 05:22.280
Mr. Zhang, today is the interns' last day.

05:22.360 --> 05:23.240
How about a few words?

05:24.080 --> 05:25.520
I do have to say something then.

05:26.120 --> 05:27.560
Lately, your performances

05:28.240 --> 05:29.760
have been really impressive.

05:29.840 --> 05:31.360
If you want to work in Yihe,

05:31.440 --> 05:32.760
come to me.

05:32.840 --> 05:35.400
I'll recommend you for a suitable post.

05:35.480 --> 05:37.360
Or I can write a recommendation letter.

05:38.480 --> 05:40.000
Also, one last thing.

05:40.080 --> 05:42.040
Gold shines wherever it is.

05:43.120 --> 05:43.960
Bling bling.

05:45.280 --> 05:46.920
- Go back to eating.
- Thank Mr. Zhang.

05:47.000 --> 05:48.640
- Say it.
- Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

05:48.720 --> 05:49.960
All right. Get back to eating.

05:50.040 --> 05:51.760
If it's not enough, buy more on me.

05:52.600 --> 05:53.920
- Okay!
- Hail, Mr. Zhang!

05:54.000 --> 05:55.360
Very good.

05:57.040 --> 05:59.200
SERVERS

06:01.240 --> 06:04.880
NUMBER OF USERS ONLINE

06:08.640 --> 06:09.800
We did it!

06:09.880 --> 06:10.840
Yes!

06:10.920 --> 06:11.880
Jiaxu!

06:12.680 --> 06:13.840
Our hard work paid off.

06:14.680 --> 06:15.720
Listen up, guys.

06:16.280 --> 06:17.400
As of now,

06:17.480 --> 06:19.480
the recent performance data

06:19.560 --> 06:20.880
has exceeded our projected targets

06:20.960 --> 06:22.120
by a large margin.

06:22.200 --> 06:23.240
As you can see,

06:23.320 --> 06:25.360
the current number is still increasing.

06:25.440 --> 06:27.280
This is the best version we have had

06:27.360 --> 06:28.880
in more than two years.

06:28.960 --> 06:30.800
Let's give ourselves a round of applause!

06:37.720 --> 06:39.000
Thank you,

06:39.080 --> 06:41.080
colleagues of A Dream of Jianghu,

06:41.800 --> 06:43.840
for your hard work throughout this year.

06:44.440 --> 06:46.360
For this great masterpiece,

06:46.440 --> 06:48.520
I can't even count how many late nights

06:48.600 --> 06:49.880
and extra hours you've worked.

06:50.440 --> 06:53.320
Today, our game is officially launched!

06:53.400 --> 06:54.360
It's worth celebrating!

06:54.920 --> 06:57.680
Let's raise our cups.

06:57.760 --> 06:58.760
Cheers!

06:58.840 --> 07:00.760
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

07:01.880 --> 07:02.880
Bonus!

07:04.160 --> 07:05.080
I didn't catch that.

07:07.480 --> 07:09.400
We've prepared food. Help yourselves.

07:09.480 --> 07:10.520
Okay, Li Xun.

07:11.200 --> 07:12.480
You have to get the last word in.

07:27.680 --> 07:28.680
Xiaoyu,

07:28.760 --> 07:31.200
today is my last day of interning.

07:31.280 --> 07:34.000
This is a gift for you.

07:37.280 --> 07:38.360
Thank you for your help.

07:38.440 --> 07:40.040
When I first started working here,

07:40.120 --> 07:41.480
I was clumsy and careless.

07:42.400 --> 07:43.680
Over the past month,

07:43.760 --> 07:45.200
I've really learned a lot.

07:47.160 --> 07:48.120
There's one more thing.

07:50.840 --> 07:52.440
I never stole anyone's boyfriend.

07:57.760 --> 07:59.080
You know Jiang Ying, right?

08:01.320 --> 08:03.240
If you are good friends with her,

08:03.320 --> 08:05.600
you can accompany her
to see a psychologist.

08:06.320 --> 08:07.480
I think it will be helpful

08:07.560 --> 08:08.800
for her.

08:09.680 --> 08:11.600
You'll also learn
about the actual situation.

08:15.800 --> 08:16.760
Thank you.

08:25.000 --> 08:26.160
It's white.

08:27.440 --> 08:28.800
You've worked hard, Li Xun.

08:28.880 --> 08:29.840
You too, Siyun.

08:30.520 --> 08:32.840
Xiaoduan, I have to thank you

08:32.919 --> 08:34.000
for your persistence

08:34.080 --> 08:35.559
on the Celestial Progression System.

08:35.640 --> 08:37.559
It's not just my accomplishment.

08:37.640 --> 08:39.000
It's mainly the result

08:39.080 --> 08:40.360
of everyone's concerted efforts

08:40.440 --> 08:41.679
and hard work.

08:43.640 --> 08:44.480
Previously,

08:45.040 --> 08:46.360
all I needed to do

08:46.440 --> 08:47.920
was follow your arrangements

08:48.000 --> 08:48.920
and work accordingly.

08:49.000 --> 08:50.640
I didn't have to consider anything else.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.760
But this experience made me realize

08:53.320 --> 08:55.360
that coordinating the work
of so many people

08:55.920 --> 08:57.160
is quite challenging.

08:57.760 --> 08:58.960
You did very well though.

09:00.320 --> 09:01.200
Anyway,

09:01.760 --> 09:03.680
I still want to thank you and Li Xun

09:03.760 --> 09:04.960
for giving me this chance.

09:05.600 --> 09:06.920
He has grown up.

09:07.480 --> 09:09.560
Do you know what his greatest virtue is?

09:09.640 --> 09:11.000
His modesty.

09:11.560 --> 09:13.360
Now you trust my judgment, don't you?

09:13.960 --> 09:16.720
I brought such talent back to Yihe.

09:18.440 --> 09:19.320
Xiaoduan.

09:20.440 --> 09:22.120
We have something to tell you too.

09:22.920 --> 09:23.840
As you know,

09:23.920 --> 09:25.440
our former chief programmer left

09:26.000 --> 09:27.920
and his position has remained vacant.

09:28.920 --> 09:31.080
Li Xun and I
have been discussing this lately.

09:31.640 --> 09:33.440
We want to recommend you

09:33.520 --> 09:34.920
for this position in our company.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.840
We still need to apply with headquarters.

09:36.920 --> 09:38.920
Do you think you're up for it?

09:41.400 --> 09:43.200
But my qualifications…

09:43.280 --> 09:45.960
Qualifications don't represent
one's capabilities.

09:46.040 --> 09:47.800
We both believe in you.

09:47.880 --> 09:49.920
However, it's not finalized yet.

09:50.000 --> 09:52.080
We have to wait for approval
from headquarters.

09:52.160 --> 09:53.360
Anyway,

09:53.920 --> 09:55.160
I don't think it will be an issue.

09:55.240 --> 09:56.240
Wait for our good news.

09:56.960 --> 09:58.080
Okay.

09:58.160 --> 10:00.240
In that case, thank you in advance.

10:00.320 --> 10:01.440
No need to thank us.

10:01.520 --> 10:02.800
You've been busy for so long.

10:02.880 --> 10:04.240
Do you have any plans after this?

10:05.840 --> 10:07.200
I plan

10:07.280 --> 10:09.880
to make it up to my girlfriend.

10:10.760 --> 10:12.040
I want to take her on a trip.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.800
That's a great idea.

10:13.880 --> 10:15.400
Do you want me to give you some ideas?

10:16.080 --> 10:17.600
Don't give him any lousy ideas.

10:17.680 --> 10:19.440
They're young people in love.

10:19.520 --> 10:21.040
Your old-fashioned ideas

10:21.120 --> 10:22.280
won't be helpful.

10:22.360 --> 10:24.360
Wait, does age matter in love?

10:24.440 --> 10:25.600
What?

10:27.640 --> 10:28.920
Yes, it does.

10:30.560 --> 10:32.360
I'll leave you two lovebirds to it.

10:32.440 --> 10:34.440
To pamper your girl,

10:34.520 --> 10:35.640
just buy the best for her.

10:38.840 --> 10:40.280
It's the Dream Castle.

10:44.200 --> 10:46.240
But I played this when I was a kid.

10:47.520 --> 10:48.400
That's fine.

10:49.800 --> 10:51.480
They also have

10:51.560 --> 10:53.040
the biggest carousel in Yihe.

10:53.120 --> 10:54.760
It will make me dizzy.

10:57.640 --> 11:00.360
If you find these rides too boring,

11:00.440 --> 11:01.560
they also have…

11:03.880 --> 11:06.080
There are more thrilling rides.

11:07.480 --> 11:08.640
I'll get scared.

11:12.200 --> 11:13.880
Then have a look at this hotel.

11:13.960 --> 11:14.920
I found it online.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.240
It has a very high rating.

11:16.320 --> 11:17.960
All guests gave positive feedback.

11:18.040 --> 11:19.200
Many of them return.

11:19.280 --> 11:20.160
Most importantly,

11:20.240 --> 11:22.080
it's very close to the amusement park.

11:22.160 --> 11:23.800
Whenever you feel tired,

11:23.880 --> 11:25.360
we can go back to the hotel to rest.

11:25.440 --> 11:27.160
I won't get tired.

11:29.440 --> 11:31.400
In this case, staying in this hotel

11:31.480 --> 11:32.400
would be a waste.

11:41.520 --> 11:43.000
So do you dislike

11:43.680 --> 11:45.120
this amusement park

11:45.200 --> 11:46.320
or this hotel?

11:47.240 --> 11:48.360
I don't like either one.

11:53.160 --> 11:54.000
Actually,

11:55.840 --> 11:57.440
it's not that I find camping a bad idea.

11:57.520 --> 11:59.200
My main concern is that

11:59.280 --> 12:01.760
a campsite usually has many insects

12:01.840 --> 12:03.400
and maybe even venomous snakes.

12:03.480 --> 12:05.960
I'm more worried
about how you will wash up there.

12:06.040 --> 12:06.920
Moreover,

12:07.000 --> 12:08.840
if it suddenly starts raining there,

12:08.920 --> 12:10.040
there won't be any shelter.

12:10.640 --> 12:12.080
I don't want you to have a hard time.

12:12.160 --> 12:13.520
Then have you considered this?

12:13.600 --> 12:16.520
If we go to the places you've planned,

12:16.600 --> 12:18.840
we have to pay for the fuel to get there.

12:19.920 --> 12:21.160
When we get there,

12:21.240 --> 12:23.040
we have to buy amusement park tickets.

12:23.120 --> 12:24.800
Food and drinks in the park

12:25.280 --> 12:26.240
will cost money too.

12:26.800 --> 12:29.320
And just now, you showed me

12:29.400 --> 12:30.960
some package for two.

12:31.040 --> 12:31.960
It…

12:32.040 --> 12:33.440
It doesn't have much to offer.

12:33.520 --> 12:34.880
Why is it so expensive?

12:34.960 --> 12:36.000
Then there's this hotel.

12:36.600 --> 12:38.440
I don't think it's even necessary.

12:38.520 --> 12:40.360
We just moved into this new flat.

12:40.880 --> 12:43.000
If we spend money on these things,

12:44.120 --> 12:45.040
then…

12:46.080 --> 12:48.280
So it's not that you dislike those places.

12:48.760 --> 12:50.680
You don't want me to waste money.

12:50.760 --> 12:51.920
That's not true.

12:52.000 --> 12:52.920
I…

12:54.000 --> 12:55.240
I never wanted to go.

13:01.520 --> 13:03.560
I just want to go camping.

13:03.640 --> 13:04.960
Why can't we just go?

13:05.040 --> 13:07.240
I've already planned it.

13:07.320 --> 13:09.360
Look at all these things I've prepared.

13:10.160 --> 13:11.800
Mosquito repellent,

13:11.880 --> 13:13.760
ambiance lights, napkins,
wet wipes, trash bags,

13:13.840 --> 13:16.280
cards, board games, flowers,
baskets, and a bubble blower.

13:16.360 --> 13:18.640
I have everything we might need ready.

13:18.720 --> 13:20.760
So why can't we go?

13:23.880 --> 13:25.760
You're so thoroughly prepared.

13:29.400 --> 13:30.640
It's my first time camping.

13:30.720 --> 13:33.080
Of course I need to cover all my bases.

13:33.160 --> 13:34.520
It's best to be prepared.

13:37.080 --> 13:39.160
Imagine this.

13:39.680 --> 13:42.040
We'll bring all these items with us.

13:42.120 --> 13:44.640
We can set up the tent together

13:45.920 --> 13:50.400
and put up camp chairs and a table.

13:50.480 --> 13:52.080
Then we'll sit there.

13:52.160 --> 13:53.760
It will feel great, won't it?

13:53.840 --> 13:55.440
We'll listen to the sound of the waves

13:55.520 --> 13:56.840
and enjoy the sea breeze.

13:56.920 --> 13:59.160
We'll wait for the sunset

13:59.240 --> 14:00.680
and watch the sunrise.

14:00.760 --> 14:01.600
At night,

14:01.680 --> 14:03.920
there will be many stars filling the sky.

14:04.480 --> 14:05.640
The most important thing is that

14:06.880 --> 14:08.400
it will be just the two of us.

14:12.880 --> 14:14.120
If we go to the amusement park,

14:14.200 --> 14:15.360
it will be noisy.

14:16.480 --> 14:17.920
But if we go camping,

14:18.480 --> 14:20.040
it will be just the two of us.

14:20.920 --> 14:21.800
I think

14:23.720 --> 14:24.800
it will be very romantic.

14:31.600 --> 14:33.400
What you just said

14:35.640 --> 14:37.440
does sound tempting.

14:39.200 --> 14:41.520
Then beach camping it is!

14:48.720 --> 14:50.120
- We'll do that.
- Really?

14:50.200 --> 14:52.120
Tomorrow morning at seven,

14:52.200 --> 14:53.520
we will set out together.

14:53.600 --> 14:55.520
I'll get up at six to pack.

14:55.600 --> 14:56.560
- No, five.
- What?

14:56.640 --> 14:57.560
I'll wake you up at four.

14:57.640 --> 14:59.400
Seven? That early?

14:59.480 --> 15:00.480
Is it early?

15:01.240 --> 15:03.640
I don't even plan to sleep tonight!

15:05.400 --> 15:07.720
I'll check if I missed anything.

15:12.680 --> 15:13.560
This…

15:21.520 --> 15:23.960
CHAPTER 22, RESPLENDENT

15:24.040 --> 15:25.960
SEE THE STARS WITH YOU

15:34.040 --> 15:36.320
Our first travel plan

15:37.640 --> 15:39.120
is ruined just like this.

15:59.240 --> 16:01.320
We need to speed up

16:01.400 --> 16:02.960
because the light

16:03.040 --> 16:04.520
indicates that it's getting late.

16:04.600 --> 16:06.640
It will be dangerous at night.
Let's hurry.

16:06.720 --> 16:07.960
- Then let's get started.
- Okay.

16:11.920 --> 16:13.680
Here.

16:30.360 --> 16:31.280
That's it.

16:31.360 --> 16:32.320
Why is it stuck?

16:32.400 --> 16:34.360
We'll screw from beneath. Right?

16:34.440 --> 16:35.440
The screw.

16:38.160 --> 16:39.000
Pull me.

17:08.119 --> 17:09.280
I'm going to answer my phone.

17:18.920 --> 17:19.960
Who is calling?

17:22.040 --> 17:23.040
My mom.

17:27.240 --> 17:28.760
Get out. I'm going inside.

17:28.840 --> 17:30.120
Hurry. Get out.

17:30.200 --> 17:31.480
I'll be inside.

17:34.920 --> 17:35.760
Get out.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.280
Zhizhi.

17:42.360 --> 17:43.200
Mom.

17:43.680 --> 17:44.760
Where are you?

17:45.880 --> 17:46.840
I'm at…

17:47.640 --> 17:48.960
Well, see for yourself.

17:49.040 --> 17:50.360
Why does it look like

17:51.280 --> 17:52.280
you're in a tent?

17:52.360 --> 17:53.400
Bingo!

17:53.480 --> 17:54.640
I'm camping.

17:55.520 --> 17:56.560
It's so comfortable.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.520
Are you camping?

17:59.160 --> 18:00.320
Dear!

18:00.400 --> 18:01.560
- Have some fruit.
- Hurry.

18:01.640 --> 18:03.200
- Your dad is here.
- Where is she?

18:03.280 --> 18:04.920
Look. She's in a tent.

18:05.000 --> 18:06.880
Zhizhi, where are you camping?

18:08.920 --> 18:10.480
I am…

18:10.560 --> 18:12.720
at my friend's flat.

18:13.760 --> 18:15.320
Did you set up a tent inside?

18:16.320 --> 18:18.320
We were supposed to go camping

18:18.400 --> 18:19.680
by the beach today.

18:19.760 --> 18:20.800
But it's raining,

18:20.880 --> 18:23.120
so we're camping at home.

18:23.200 --> 18:24.360
It's also fun.

18:24.440 --> 18:25.640
Show me around.

18:25.720 --> 18:27.920
Your dad and I want
to take time to go camping.

18:28.000 --> 18:29.000
That's right.

18:29.520 --> 18:31.480
Show you around? Do you want me to?

18:32.040 --> 18:33.280
I'll flip the camera, okay?

18:33.360 --> 18:34.680
I'm doing it now.

18:38.920 --> 18:40.160
Can you see?

18:41.280 --> 18:42.160
Look.

18:42.240 --> 18:44.320
Look. Out there, it's…

18:44.880 --> 18:46.240
It's raining.

18:46.320 --> 18:47.160
Can you see it?

18:48.600 --> 18:49.640
Look.

18:49.720 --> 18:50.720
It's raining.

18:52.280 --> 18:53.960
This is the tent.

18:54.040 --> 18:55.120
This is

18:55.200 --> 18:57.240
the tent we set up.

18:57.320 --> 18:59.200
Over here is the dining room.

18:59.280 --> 19:00.240
Can you see it?

19:03.320 --> 19:04.720
That is

19:04.800 --> 19:05.800
the kitchen.

19:05.880 --> 19:06.760
This is the kitchen.

19:07.360 --> 19:08.400
Right over here.

19:10.880 --> 19:12.360
The bedrooms are over there.

19:14.640 --> 19:15.880
That's all.

19:16.360 --> 19:17.560
And then…

19:19.080 --> 19:20.520
- What happened?
- What happened?

19:20.600 --> 19:21.480
I'm fine.

19:21.560 --> 19:22.760
I…

19:23.280 --> 19:24.600
I accidentally tripped

19:24.680 --> 19:25.720
over some equipment.

19:25.800 --> 19:26.680
Be careful.

19:26.760 --> 19:28.760
Are you sure it was the equipment

19:28.840 --> 19:30.560
instead of a dog?

19:32.520 --> 19:34.080
Sang Yan, I wasn't talking to you,

19:34.160 --> 19:35.360
so don't speak.

19:35.440 --> 19:37.560
Don't be mean.

19:37.640 --> 19:38.680
Zhizhi.

19:39.280 --> 19:40.920
You camping inside

19:41.000 --> 19:42.360
reminds me of when I was a child

19:42.440 --> 19:44.120
and set up tents in the living room.

19:44.200 --> 19:45.240
It felt so safe.

19:45.720 --> 19:46.600
Isn't it fun?

19:47.520 --> 19:48.720
Yes, it's fun.

19:48.800 --> 19:50.040
If you also want to have fun,

19:50.840 --> 19:51.720
you can

19:53.200 --> 19:55.240
set one up in the garden.

19:57.400 --> 19:58.280
Zhizhi.

19:58.920 --> 20:00.120
If you want

20:00.200 --> 20:02.040
to do another internship next summer,

20:02.600 --> 20:04.120
come back to Nanwu.

20:04.800 --> 20:05.720
Your mom

20:06.280 --> 20:07.400
misses you

20:07.480 --> 20:08.800
and talks about you all the time.

20:09.400 --> 20:10.560
She can't even sleep well.

20:12.040 --> 20:13.040
Come back home.

20:13.760 --> 20:14.760
Zhizhi.

20:14.840 --> 20:16.480
Come home after you graduate, okay?

20:16.560 --> 20:17.960
So you can be closer to me.

20:20.440 --> 20:22.400
I'll think about it

20:22.480 --> 20:23.520
when I graduate.

20:23.600 --> 20:24.640
It's still too early.

20:25.920 --> 20:27.360
You should get back

20:27.440 --> 20:28.640
to what you were doing.

20:28.720 --> 20:30.760
We're going to finish setting up the tent.

20:31.240 --> 20:32.600
Okay, go have fun.

20:32.680 --> 20:33.840
Enjoy yourselves.

20:33.920 --> 20:35.000
Bye.

20:39.440 --> 20:40.760
Did you hit yourself?

20:44.040 --> 20:45.240
I'm fine.

20:45.320 --> 20:46.280
Let's continue.

20:46.920 --> 20:47.880
Okay.

20:48.760 --> 20:49.600
Come on.

20:51.080 --> 20:52.720
It's still standing.

20:53.600 --> 20:54.680
You've improved.

20:55.200 --> 20:56.680
It's your turn now.

21:05.160 --> 21:06.960
It's a little too easy.

21:07.040 --> 21:08.040
I'm pulling it.

21:19.200 --> 21:20.440
That was fast.

21:20.520 --> 21:21.520
This one.

21:21.600 --> 21:22.520
How about this one?

21:23.160 --> 21:24.600
Just listen to me, okay?

21:25.480 --> 21:26.400
Yes.

21:35.520 --> 21:36.920
Pick a punishment.

21:37.000 --> 21:38.160
Let me shuffle these.

21:41.360 --> 21:42.440
This one.

21:45.440 --> 21:46.560
I'm doing pretty well.

22:14.320 --> 22:15.400
SEPTEMBER 1ST, SATURDAY

22:15.480 --> 22:17.640
WE LISTENED TO THE SOUND OF WAVES,
FELT THE SEA BREEZE,

22:17.720 --> 22:19.560
WATCHED THE SUNSET,
AND WAITED FOR THE SUNRISE.

22:19.640 --> 22:20.560
BUT MOST IMPORTANTLY,

22:20.640 --> 22:22.240
IT WAS ROMANTIC
WITH JUST THE TWO OF US.

22:28.520 --> 22:29.360
Look.

22:30.600 --> 22:31.680
This one.

22:31.760 --> 22:33.400
Ladies,

22:33.480 --> 22:34.920
did you see the campus announcement?

22:35.000 --> 22:37.240
- What?
- Yihe University Design Competition.

22:37.320 --> 22:39.040
I didn't see it. Did you?

22:41.720 --> 22:43.080
What do you think?

22:43.160 --> 22:44.720
I think it's legit.

22:44.800 --> 22:47.240
It's highly worthwhile this year.

22:47.320 --> 22:48.640
Many companies are involved.

22:48.720 --> 22:49.600
That's right.

22:50.160 --> 22:51.080
Are you interested?

22:53.400 --> 22:54.640
I want

22:54.720 --> 22:56.360
to gain some competition experience.

22:57.080 --> 22:58.720
I don't care if I can get shortlisted

22:58.800 --> 22:59.680
or win a prize.

22:59.760 --> 23:01.080
- It doesn't matter.
- That's right.

23:01.160 --> 23:02.520
But after we graduate,

23:02.600 --> 23:04.080
it will beef up our resumes.

23:04.160 --> 23:05.240
That's what I think too.

23:05.920 --> 23:08.240
Sangsang, I'm so impressed with you.

23:08.320 --> 23:10.520
How do you balance life so easily?

23:10.600 --> 23:12.520
You have love and a career.

23:14.200 --> 23:15.800
Sangsang isn't like you,

23:15.880 --> 23:17.520
a simple love creature.

23:17.600 --> 23:19.160
Me? I'm not like that.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.200
Then…

23:21.560 --> 23:22.520
Are you…

23:22.600 --> 23:23.960
Of course I'm taking part.

23:24.040 --> 23:25.520
I came to tell you guys about it.

23:26.720 --> 23:27.680
Ning Wei,

23:27.760 --> 23:29.080
you…

23:29.640 --> 23:30.520
Forget it.

23:30.600 --> 23:32.320
Wangwang, will you be participating?

23:33.200 --> 23:34.440
I…

23:34.520 --> 23:35.720
I won't.

23:35.800 --> 23:37.120
I'll wait until next year.

23:37.200 --> 23:38.480
That's fine too.

23:40.480 --> 23:41.760
It's just the two of us.

23:45.800 --> 23:46.880
- Sign up.
- Sign up.

23:46.960 --> 23:48.640
- Hurry.
- Is it on the official site?

23:48.720 --> 23:50.480
Yes, we sign up on the school's website.

23:56.800 --> 23:57.960
Wangwang.

23:58.040 --> 23:59.440
Why did you want to see me?

23:59.520 --> 24:00.640
I have something to give you.

24:01.160 --> 24:03.160
- Here.
- What's this?

24:03.720 --> 24:05.440
It's an edited version of your interview.

24:07.880 --> 24:09.280
Thank you. I'll watch it.

24:09.360 --> 24:10.320
It's nothing.

24:10.800 --> 24:11.920
By the way,

24:12.000 --> 24:13.240
did you submit your assignment?

24:14.800 --> 24:16.480
Thank you for accepting my interview.

24:17.400 --> 24:18.840
Well, if you don't mind,

24:18.920 --> 24:20.000
I'm going back to training.

24:21.640 --> 24:23.360
Can you wait a minute?

24:24.520 --> 24:26.200
I have something else to tell you.

24:30.800 --> 24:31.680
Actually,

24:32.600 --> 24:33.920
I like you.

24:35.360 --> 24:36.840
Ever since our first meeting

24:36.920 --> 24:38.200
when you helped me out,

24:38.800 --> 24:40.160
I've had feelings for you.

24:40.760 --> 24:42.880
As we spent more time together,

24:42.960 --> 24:44.760
I began to like you more and more.

24:48.200 --> 24:49.560
I…

24:49.640 --> 24:51.320
You don't have to rush to answer me.

24:51.400 --> 24:53.920
I just want to tell you how I feel.

24:54.000 --> 24:55.800
I admire you a lot

24:55.880 --> 24:57.400
and really like you.

24:59.080 --> 25:01.080
So don't feel pressured.

25:01.160 --> 25:03.440
We will still be good friends.

25:04.560 --> 25:05.480
Right?

25:12.920 --> 25:13.920
That's all.

25:14.400 --> 25:15.400
I'll go now.

25:16.320 --> 25:17.400
Okay.

25:22.360 --> 25:23.720
I confessed my feelings.

25:23.800 --> 25:25.960
It's not so hard after all.

25:39.200 --> 25:40.760
What's wrong, Sangsang?

25:44.400 --> 25:46.040
There are too many themes

25:46.120 --> 25:47.240
that I want to do.

25:47.320 --> 25:48.800
I still haven't picked one yet.

25:50.600 --> 25:52.440
It's okay. Take your time to think.

25:52.520 --> 25:54.520
You can look through other materials,

25:54.600 --> 25:56.760
books, and whatnot for inspiration.

25:59.120 --> 26:00.240
What about you?

26:01.000 --> 26:01.840
Me?

26:02.920 --> 26:05.760
I'm working on The Century's Star Wars.

26:07.360 --> 26:08.920
That's so cool.

26:09.000 --> 26:09.920
Not bad, right?

26:10.560 --> 26:12.560
I've been planning it for a long time.

26:12.640 --> 26:14.240
It's a prequel story for the game

26:14.320 --> 26:16.040
that I want to design in the future.

26:16.520 --> 26:18.040
I'm quite confident about it.

26:18.920 --> 26:19.920
That sounds great.

26:22.000 --> 26:23.240
I'll get back to brainstorming.

26:26.760 --> 26:29.080
If you don't have any ideas,
don't try to force it.

26:29.160 --> 26:30.240
We still have time.

26:30.880 --> 26:33.080
Go home and relax
for the National Day holiday.

26:33.160 --> 26:35.120
Maybe inspiration will come then.

26:38.560 --> 26:39.480
Get back to your idea.

26:57.800 --> 26:59.840
I'm already in the car.

27:05.520 --> 27:06.840
I remember someone said

27:06.920 --> 27:08.120
that he would not pick me up.

27:08.200 --> 27:09.840
He also said

27:09.920 --> 27:11.440
that he didn't want to see me.

27:13.440 --> 27:14.320
Ask Duan Jiaxu

27:14.400 --> 27:15.720
what is wrong with him.

27:16.400 --> 27:17.280
Why?

27:17.360 --> 27:19.440
This morning, he called me
three consecutive times.

27:19.520 --> 27:21.520
I silenced my phone,
but he ordered takeout for me.

27:21.600 --> 27:23.120
Do you know what was written on it?

27:23.720 --> 27:24.720
He added a note that said,

27:24.800 --> 27:27.320
"My boyfriend is in poor health.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.640
Please make sure he gets up to eat

27:29.720 --> 27:31.480
or the consequences will be dire.

27:31.560 --> 27:32.440
Thank you."

27:34.680 --> 27:35.800
I was speechless.

27:36.640 --> 27:38.560
Maybe he just wanted you to get up

27:38.640 --> 27:39.760
and have breakfast.

27:39.840 --> 27:40.800
It's healthy for you.

27:40.880 --> 27:42.360
That had better be the case.

27:42.960 --> 27:44.840
But I can understand his concern.

27:44.920 --> 27:46.480
He was just worried

27:46.560 --> 27:48.480
that no one would pick his girlfriend up.

27:48.560 --> 27:49.920
If he's so worried about you,

27:50.000 --> 27:52.480
why did he trouble me
instead of coming with you?

27:52.560 --> 27:53.560
He's very busy.

27:53.640 --> 27:55.280
Otherwise, he would've come with me.

27:55.360 --> 27:57.160
Listen, I want you to text him and say,

27:57.240 --> 27:58.840
"Just you wait."

28:01.360 --> 28:02.240
Why?

28:03.240 --> 28:04.320
What are you going to do?

28:04.880 --> 28:05.760
I'll beat him up.

28:07.160 --> 28:08.320
I'm driving here.

28:08.400 --> 28:09.600
Stay still, will you?

28:10.280 --> 28:11.440
Nuisance.

28:13.960 --> 28:16.160
Shoot. I'm dead meat.

28:16.720 --> 28:17.920
What's wrong?

28:19.560 --> 28:21.160
I can't believe I forgot about this.

28:21.240 --> 28:22.600
- What is it?
- Get me directions.

28:22.680 --> 28:24.200
Your crispy taro-crusted duck!

28:24.280 --> 28:25.360
I forgot to buy it.

28:25.840 --> 28:26.920
I thought it was important.

28:27.000 --> 28:28.400
Pull up directions for me now.

28:28.960 --> 28:30.240
I don't have to eat it today.

28:30.320 --> 28:32.440
No way! Mom will scold me again!

28:33.160 --> 28:34.760
Get directions for me. We'll buy it now.

28:34.840 --> 28:35.800
Take me home first.

28:35.880 --> 28:37.120
Then you can go and buy it.

28:52.120 --> 28:54.160
You've been fussing
with your camera for two days.

28:54.240 --> 28:55.280
Do you know how to use it?

28:55.360 --> 28:56.760
I need to get the hang of it.

28:56.840 --> 28:58.600
When Zhizhi is back, I'll take you two out

28:58.680 --> 29:00.040
and take beautiful pictures.

29:00.120 --> 29:01.320
Come on, dear. Look at me.

29:03.280 --> 29:05.400
One, two, three.

29:05.480 --> 29:06.680
Beautiful.

29:06.760 --> 29:08.000
Try another pose.

29:08.080 --> 29:09.240
Another pose?

29:09.320 --> 29:10.640
Okay. One, two, three.

29:11.400 --> 29:12.440
Gorgeous.

29:14.640 --> 29:15.880
- How about this?
- Okay.

29:18.800 --> 29:20.320
You showed up out of nowhere!

29:20.400 --> 29:21.800
You startled me!

29:21.880 --> 29:23.360
I just wanted to give you a surprise.

29:24.200 --> 29:25.720
Dad, did you get a new camera?

29:25.800 --> 29:27.880
- Yes. How about a triple shot?
- He just bought it.

29:27.960 --> 29:28.840
- Okay.
- All right.

29:28.920 --> 29:30.200
- One.
- Okay. One.

29:31.360 --> 29:32.240
Okay, two.

29:32.320 --> 29:33.400
Give me a different pose.

29:33.480 --> 29:34.400
Okay.

29:34.480 --> 29:35.560
And another one.

29:37.000 --> 29:38.000
I'm so blessed.

29:38.080 --> 29:39.240
My beautiful ladies.

29:39.840 --> 29:40.720
Where's your brother?

29:41.760 --> 29:42.800
He said he was going

29:42.880 --> 29:44.320
to buy the crispy taro-crusted duck.

29:44.400 --> 29:45.880
I said to buy it before fetching you.

29:45.960 --> 29:47.280
He just never listens.

29:47.360 --> 29:48.320
You need to talk to him.

29:48.400 --> 29:49.400
- He's so careless.
- I will.

29:49.480 --> 29:51.040
- I'll go change my shoes.
- Okay.

29:51.120 --> 29:52.760
Come down for dinner afterward, okay?

30:10.200 --> 30:11.040
Hello?

30:12.280 --> 30:13.440
What are you doing?

30:18.440 --> 30:19.480
I'm missing you.

30:21.920 --> 30:23.320
I miss you too.

30:23.400 --> 30:24.520
Have you eaten?

30:25.320 --> 30:26.240
Not yet.

30:27.080 --> 30:28.000
What about you?

30:28.520 --> 30:29.960
Neither have I.

30:30.040 --> 30:32.000
When are you going to eat?

30:32.080 --> 30:33.640
Not until I finish up some work.

30:33.720 --> 30:34.560
Zhizhi.

30:39.440 --> 30:41.040
I'll call you back later.

30:41.720 --> 30:42.920
Okay.

30:44.120 --> 30:45.400
- I brought you some fruit.
- Okay.

30:45.480 --> 30:46.840
- Thank you, Mom.
- It's nothing.

30:46.920 --> 30:48.960
I'll call you when it's time for dinner.

31:08.680 --> 31:11.800
Sorry, my mom suddenly came in.

31:11.880 --> 31:14.360
SANG ZHI

31:16.320 --> 31:17.360
It's okay.

31:18.040 --> 31:20.240
Spend more time with your parents.

31:20.320 --> 31:22.080
After I finish my work,

31:22.160 --> 31:23.480
I'll fly over to see you.

31:23.960 --> 31:24.920
Wait for me.

31:25.000 --> 31:30.320
DUAN JIAXU

31:30.400 --> 31:33.280
SANG ZHI

32:04.480 --> 32:06.240
Sorry, little fox.

32:06.760 --> 32:08.320
I've locked you up for so long.

32:27.680 --> 32:30.520
I HAVE A SECRET

32:30.600 --> 32:32.600
I SEEM TO HAVE FALLEN FOR HIM

32:32.680 --> 32:35.320
DUAN JIAXU

32:37.520 --> 32:39.800
JIAXU, HAPPY NEW YEAR

32:41.280 --> 32:42.840
MAKE A LOT OF MONEY

32:42.920 --> 32:44.920
AND HELP HIM PAY OFF HIS DEBTS

32:47.040 --> 32:50.240
MY DREAM

32:53.920 --> 32:55.160
Duan Jiaxu.

32:56.200 --> 32:57.040
I am really

32:58.080 --> 32:59.600
in a relationship with you.

33:03.040 --> 33:04.400
Is Zhizhi dating someone?

33:06.360 --> 33:07.520
Who is the guy?

33:08.120 --> 33:09.040
How old is he?

33:09.120 --> 33:10.200
Is he a classmate?

33:10.800 --> 33:12.000
Calm down.

33:12.560 --> 33:13.680
I'm not sure either.

33:13.760 --> 33:15.880
What if it's not her boyfriend?

33:16.600 --> 33:18.160
He sounds like a suspicious guy.

33:19.160 --> 33:20.360
We need to find out about it.

33:21.560 --> 33:22.560
Let's go and ask her.

33:23.320 --> 33:24.240
Let's go.

33:25.160 --> 33:26.360
Do you think it's okay, dear?

33:26.440 --> 33:27.760
Yes, it's okay. Just come.

33:30.920 --> 33:32.040
I'm coming.

33:35.360 --> 33:36.360
Zhizhi.

33:38.080 --> 33:39.200
Your mom and I

33:39.680 --> 33:41.120
have something to ask you.

33:42.480 --> 33:43.440
Okay.

33:51.080 --> 33:52.560
Take a seat then.

33:52.640 --> 33:53.480
Okay.

33:55.040 --> 33:56.120
What's up?

33:58.120 --> 34:00.400
Zhizhi, be honest with me.

34:00.880 --> 34:02.720
Are you dating someone?

34:14.880 --> 34:15.920
Come on.

34:17.080 --> 34:18.400
If you're dating someone,

34:18.480 --> 34:19.880
why didn't you tell me?

34:19.960 --> 34:22.040
I called you every day.

34:22.120 --> 34:24.120
I wanted to tell you.

34:24.199 --> 34:25.280
But I wanted

34:25.360 --> 34:27.080
to tell you in person.

34:29.040 --> 34:29.960
So she's dating.

34:30.800 --> 34:32.639
Well, Zhizhi.

34:33.199 --> 34:34.239
Your…

34:35.280 --> 34:36.400
Your boyfriend, right?

34:37.080 --> 34:38.400
How old is he? Where did you meet?

34:38.480 --> 34:40.760
Is he a student?
Or did you meet him outside of campus?

34:40.840 --> 34:42.440
How is his character?

34:42.520 --> 34:43.639
Where does he study?

34:43.719 --> 34:45.159
What is his major?

34:45.239 --> 34:47.239
Zhizhi, you see,

34:47.320 --> 34:49.000
I think you're still too young.

34:49.560 --> 34:51.600
How about you wait until you've graduated?

34:51.679 --> 34:53.480
If you're in a relationship now,

34:53.560 --> 34:56.280
when you graduate,
you'll have to settle down there.

34:56.360 --> 34:57.520
Have you ever considered this?

34:57.600 --> 35:00.000
Will your boyfriend come back
to Nanwu with you?

35:00.080 --> 35:01.200
- Am I right?
- Yes.

35:01.280 --> 35:02.920
The main issue is that you're too young.

35:03.000 --> 35:04.400
You haven't graduated.

35:04.480 --> 35:05.760
Why don't you wait until--

35:05.840 --> 35:07.680
I'll go check if Sang Yan is back.

35:07.760 --> 35:09.000
Sang Yan.

35:11.520 --> 35:13.440
So who is she dating?

35:13.520 --> 35:14.880
Calm down.

35:14.960 --> 35:16.240
She's very tight-lipped.

35:16.320 --> 35:18.080
I don't know who she is dating either.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.400
You rushed into talking to her.

35:20.480 --> 35:21.800
You've scared her.

35:21.880 --> 35:23.440
How could she be open with us?

35:25.840 --> 35:26.880
You have a point.

35:27.360 --> 35:29.000
But anyway, we must keep an eye on her

35:29.480 --> 35:30.720
when it comes to dating.

35:32.400 --> 35:33.680
How?

35:33.760 --> 35:34.760
She's out of town.

35:37.960 --> 35:38.960
Everyone says that bugs

35:39.040 --> 35:40.840
are also a part of the gaming experience.

35:42.000 --> 35:43.880
But we've tested it many times.

35:43.960 --> 35:46.280
Why are there still so many strange bugs?

35:47.240 --> 35:48.120
Seriously.

35:54.480 --> 35:55.600
I'm leaving now.

35:55.680 --> 35:56.840
During the holiday,

35:56.920 --> 35:58.160
I'll be counting on you guys.

35:59.200 --> 36:00.360
If you encounter

36:00.440 --> 36:02.240
any unresolved or unfamiliar bugs,

36:02.320 --> 36:03.840
ask Zhang Sen for help.

36:05.400 --> 36:06.480
Okay.

36:07.040 --> 36:08.400
- Xiaobai.
- Yes.

36:08.480 --> 36:10.840
While I'm away, I'll have to trouble you.

36:10.920 --> 36:12.800
Email me everyone's daily tasks

36:12.880 --> 36:14.760
and issues that you encounter.

36:14.840 --> 36:17.400
If there are any issues you can't solve,

36:17.480 --> 36:18.680
just contact me at any time.

36:18.760 --> 36:20.160
You can count on me.

36:21.480 --> 36:22.520
Thank you, guys.

36:22.600 --> 36:23.680
Don't worry, Jiaxu.

36:23.760 --> 36:26.080
For the next few days,
focus on being with your girlfriend.

36:26.160 --> 36:27.760
We promise not to contact you.

36:27.840 --> 36:28.800
- Right?
- Yes.

36:28.880 --> 36:30.080
- Yes.
- That would be best.

36:30.160 --> 36:31.120
Of course.

36:31.200 --> 36:33.000
- Bye.
- Bye.

36:37.640 --> 36:38.520
Wait, Jiaxu!

36:39.800 --> 36:41.040
There's another error.

36:47.880 --> 36:48.760
Bye.

36:54.360 --> 36:55.520
Come in.

36:57.640 --> 36:58.480
Sang Yan.

36:58.560 --> 36:59.440
What do you want?

37:08.200 --> 37:09.480
Are you playing a game?

37:09.560 --> 37:10.880
Yes, and I'm losing.

37:10.960 --> 37:13.160
But you're so smart. How could you lose?

37:14.520 --> 37:15.800
All right. What is it?

37:16.760 --> 37:17.760
You must be tired.

37:18.640 --> 37:20.200
That's usually how gaming is.

37:20.280 --> 37:21.480
It's exhausting.

37:21.560 --> 37:22.960
Your shoulders must be aching.

37:23.520 --> 37:24.880
Your hands as well, right?

37:27.360 --> 37:29.240
What are you up to?

37:29.320 --> 37:31.200
You look like you're ready.

37:31.680 --> 37:32.720
Are you going out?

37:33.520 --> 37:34.600
It's none of your business.

37:37.840 --> 37:39.000
Are you going out for dinner?

37:41.320 --> 37:42.560
What will you have?

37:43.680 --> 37:44.960
Is it delicious?

37:46.800 --> 37:48.000
Who are you going with?

37:49.600 --> 37:51.160
Duan Jiaxu will be there. He will.

37:51.240 --> 37:53.360
So do you want to come along

37:54.040 --> 37:55.120
because Duan Jiaxu is going?

37:58.240 --> 38:00.040
I'm quite understanding, right?

38:01.040 --> 38:02.040
Mom!

38:02.120 --> 38:03.440
You…

38:03.520 --> 38:04.920
What's your problem?

38:05.000 --> 38:06.960
I'll tell Mom not to make you dinner.

38:07.040 --> 38:08.160
What the heck?

38:11.400 --> 38:13.960
I'll go get ready then.

38:14.040 --> 38:15.440
Okay, you have two minutes.

38:16.680 --> 38:17.720
Three minutes.

38:18.520 --> 38:19.600
Three minutes at most.

38:20.160 --> 38:21.040
You're so slow.

38:21.120 --> 38:22.280
Fine, five minutes!

38:23.560 --> 38:24.760
I'll wait for you downstairs.

38:25.640 --> 38:29.320
Sunshine, rainbow, and white horse

38:51.080 --> 38:52.920
Can you tone it down a little?

38:53.000 --> 38:54.960
You're smiling like a fool.

38:58.920 --> 39:00.920
Sang Yan, please focus on driving.

39:01.000 --> 39:02.160
Don't mind me, okay?

39:03.360 --> 39:04.400
I don't understand

39:04.480 --> 39:06.320
what is going on in Duan Jiaxu's head.

39:06.400 --> 39:08.120
We're eating with a bunch of guys,

39:08.200 --> 39:09.720
but he insists on taking you along.

39:10.520 --> 39:12.000
You won't take me out to dinner.

39:12.080 --> 39:13.320
He won't either.

39:13.400 --> 39:14.880
What's wrong with taking me to dinner?

39:14.960 --> 39:17.200
Well, won't you feel awkward eating

39:17.280 --> 39:18.600
with people you don't know?

39:19.080 --> 39:20.040
No.

39:20.640 --> 39:21.520
People always say

39:21.600 --> 39:23.000
others will feel awkward

39:23.080 --> 39:24.280
if I don't.

39:24.360 --> 39:26.360
You're right. I'm the one feeling awkward.

39:26.440 --> 39:27.520
That's great.

39:28.680 --> 39:29.960
In my senior year of university,

39:30.040 --> 39:32.480
I remember you pretentiously said,

39:32.560 --> 39:34.720
"I want to help you move into the new dorm

39:34.800 --> 39:37.080
or I will feel really bad."

39:37.160 --> 39:38.040
You insisted on going.

39:38.120 --> 39:39.400
Now I finally understand.

39:41.600 --> 39:42.880
Keep pretending!

39:47.320 --> 39:48.360
I don't remember that.

39:50.560 --> 39:52.840
There was one time
when our parents weren't home.

39:52.920 --> 39:55.160
You insisted on joining us for a hot pot.

39:55.240 --> 39:56.440
Duan Jiaxu and I even went

39:56.520 --> 39:58.280
to buy menstrual pads for you.

39:58.360 --> 40:00.000
I didn't insist on going at that time.

40:00.080 --> 40:01.120
- You--
- That time--

40:01.200 --> 40:02.760
It was you who insisted.

40:02.840 --> 40:05.000
No, you insisted on taking me
to eat hot pot.

40:05.080 --> 40:06.800
No, you wanted to go that time!

40:06.880 --> 40:08.840
- I didn't!
- You did!

40:10.000 --> 40:11.480
Do you think it's appropriate for you

40:11.560 --> 40:12.560
to discuss pads with me?

40:12.640 --> 40:14.880
Focus on driving and stop talking, okay?

40:16.560 --> 40:18.760
When you were little,
you called him your brother.

40:18.840 --> 40:20.520
You sounded closer to him than to me.

40:20.600 --> 40:21.760
You just don't love me at all.

40:30.080 --> 40:32.640
I was being polite.

40:33.320 --> 40:36.080
I was being respectful. Understand?

40:36.680 --> 40:38.720
Why weren't you polite
and respectful to me?

40:42.160 --> 40:43.480
I love you.

41:15.560 --> 41:16.680
Are you sleepy?

41:19.720 --> 41:22.000
I'll get the sleeping bag ready.

41:30.720 --> 41:31.840
Come on.

41:31.920 --> 41:32.840
Let's go to sleep.

41:47.200 --> 41:48.560
Which one do you want to sleep in?

41:50.920 --> 41:52.000
This one.

42:11.960 --> 42:13.360
I'll turn off the light.

42:52.480 --> 42:53.640
Good night.

43:04.360 --> 43:06.280
During the National Day holiday,

43:06.360 --> 43:07.760
I'll go back to Nanwu with you.

43:09.440 --> 43:10.920
Will you?

43:12.480 --> 43:14.240
I know you miss home.
